      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Tricky. LEVERAGED BUYOUT (8) brings the right form to this race after winning a 1400m contest at this track by 2.5 lengths. Goes well at this journey with two wins from four starts and can make the hat-trick. GARRIX (4) just missed at Oakbank 12 days ago over 1400m as a short-priced favourite and was close up at Newcastle for the Waller camp the one before. Is still a maiden but has the ability to take this out. GRINZINGER TUNDRA (5) is a former Victorian who won over a sprint first-up before a plainer effort over 1400m well supported. Fitter again and the steps up to the 1600m will suit. His best numbers would see him in the finish. PLEASING SMILE (9) brings an easy win over 1200m from Darwin and placed his only try this trip. Deserves consideration. GALLAHOP (3) has switched from a Sydney yard and monitor the betting.",
